一名代号“华强”的成员，伪装成普通顾客前往一个被巴西尼家族控制的水果摊。\n监听录音中，华强反复询问瓜贩：“这瓜保熟吗？”这一看似日常的问价，实为确认毒品藏匿状态的暗语。当瓜被一刀劈开，露出藏在蜡纸中的白货之后，录音里传来了汤普逊冲锋枪的枪声。\n本片根据该份档案整理制作，还原了这场被掩盖多年的反毒清算行动。部分画面经AI修复，", "state": 0, "duration": 197, "mission_id": 4062378, "rights": {"bp": 0, "elec": 0, "download": 0, "movie": 0, "pay": 0, "hd5": 0, "no_reprint": 1, "autoplay": 1, "ugc_pay": 0, "is_cooperation": 0, "ugc_pay_preview": 0, "no_background": 0, "arc_pay": 0, "pay_free_watch": 0}, "owner": {"mid": 498109258, "name": "蔚蓝丶羽翼", "face": "https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/c5cdba714fe63498657a5b30893df2c5f6b2cda4.jpg"}, "stat": {"aid": 116498035251359, "view": 397538, "danmaku": 762, "reply": 782, "favorite": 9595, "coin": 4148, "share": 3181, "now_rank": 0, "his_rank": 0, "like": 39176, "dislike": 0, "vt": 0, "vv": 397538, "fav_g": 0, "like_g": 0}, "dynamic": "", "cid": 38002821731, "dimension": {"width": 1280, "height": 720, "rotate": 0}, "season_id": 8023043, "short_link_v2": "https://b23.tv/BV1RGRMBUEVK", "first_frame": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/storyff/_00000zjimirgmfhvr2fyz70y5tcn4eb_firsti.jpg", "pub_location": "四川", "cover43": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/5b2f4527765f87c653e09fe2312cc90697dac411.jpg", "tidv2": 2063, "tnamev2": "鬼畜综合", "pid_v2": 1007, "pid_name_v2": "鬼畜", "bvid": "BV1RGRMBUEVK", "season_type": 0, "is_ogv": false, "ogv_info": null, "enable_vt": 0, "ai_rcmd": null, "rcmd_reason": {"content": "", "corner_mark": 0}}, {"aid": 116487129992149, "videos": 1, "tid": 210, "tname": "模玩·周边", "copyright": 1, "pic": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d00351ac0d107e41d5204895c42a0e6e2dd7cbe0.jpg", "title": "极致还原迈克尔杰克逊Billie Jean舞蹈【幕后制作】", "pubdate": 1777456800, "ctime": 1777453265, "desc": "幕后很快就来了嗷，感谢各位支撑，希望各位看得开心，有制作相关的问题也可以提出~\n\n\n动画：默铀 豌豆\n素体：Vtoys 壹号素体（非广）\n服装：豌豆\n灯光：默铀\n后期：默铀", "state": 0, "duration": 177, "mission_id": 4064283, "rights": {"bp": 0, "elec": 0, "download": 0, "movie": 0, "pay": 0, "hd5": 0, "no_reprint": 1, "autoplay": 1, "ugc_pay": 0, "is_cooperation": 1, "ugc_pay_preview": 0, "no_back